original_body_lines: SriLankan Airlines today celebrated the power of women in the airline with a flight operated by an all-female crew on Women’s Day 2023. Flight UL131 departed to Trichy on the morning and was staffed by Captain Chamika Rupasinghe; First Officer Bimalee Jeewandara; Purser Roshani Dissanayake; Cabin Supervisor Upuli Warnakula; and Flight Attendants Lakmini Dissanayake, Jayakalani Kinson and Harshi Walpola Kankanamalage.
